column5: HIT 3 TRIBS TO FIND SOME SAFE ICE TO FISH ON!!! MOST AROUND 2"BUT FOUND A GOOD SPOT WITH 5". HAD TO TRY OUT MY NEW CUSTOM MADE ICE RODS(10"S LONGER THEN STANDARD ROD) BUT THEY SAW NO ACTION TODAY!! 5HRS IN AND THEY DIDNT MOVE  LOL OH WELL ALWAYS ANOTHER DAY!!! (SEE I GET SKUNKED TOO  LOL)
Nice clean pic. I have NO doubt you'll be pulling them out in no time.

Skunked?? Hmmm...maybe I dont wanna go out with you Friday...LOL.  Just joking!  Friday is looking frigid right now... -19 for the low and -12 for the high.  Let me know if you still want to go....haha.
the colder the better where were goin bro  lol!! thurs or fri let me know what ya get off

thanks for the report CC,i told you that you caught all the bows around southern ontario,lol..lol     and yes clampet sounds like you have lots of warm clothes like myself ...ya gotta have them or its no fun...can cut your day real short the worst is getting your feet cold,,,,you are done like dinner.....stay warm cliff ....cheers guys

No problem!  I'm used to dressing in all kinds of layers for where I usually fish.  I bought a bunch of thermal clothing from Gagnon's during their 50% off sale, so I'm all set.  The colder the better where we're going??  Jeez...now you got my mind churning trying to figure it out!! LOL.  Let me know what to bring ok?  Oh yeah...Friday is the day I'm off.  Cliff
